<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="35" type="type locality">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="35">Type locality.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="35">
China. Hunan province: the course of Wu River, a sampling point at Changpu Town, Suining County, 
<geoCoordinate degrees="26" direction="north" minutes="34.59" orientation="latitude" precision="9" value="26.5765">26°34.59'N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate degrees="110" direction="east" minutes="09.19" orientation="longitude" precision="9" value="110.15317">110°09.19'E</geoCoordinate>
, 300 m a.s.l., collected by Bing Liu, March 22, 2021.
</paragraph>
