0.3 
<normalizedToken originalValue="μS">μS</normalizedToken>
∙cm-1, pH was 7.9 
<normalizedToken originalValue="±">+/-</normalizedToken>
0.1 and water temperature was 13.2 
<normalizedToken originalValue="±">+/-</normalizedToken>
0.2 °C.
</paragraph>
